      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "The Chilliwack Rock Choir is back to crank your favourites up to 11! This isn’t just any choir performance — backed by a live band, they deliver classic rock anthems with the raw energy and excitement of a full-blown rock show."
      }
